  "description": {
   "en": "Soaris, the daughter of a wealthy viscount, was 12 years old when she married Arendio, the son of a poor countess, in a political marriage. Apparently dissatisfied with this marriage, he left Soaris for military service soon after.\n\nTen years later, Soaris' family has fallen into ruin, and she decides to divorce him for the sake of Arendio, who has become a hero of the country. But when Alendio returns, he loves Soaris as if she were a different person!\n\nWhat in the world is going on, even though he hates her?\n\nA handsome romantic comedy about a wife who wants a divorce and a husband who wants to dote on her."
  },
